body_html:
Actually, I am using a server which bases on a lot of computers. And the administrators installed several versions of tensorflow as 'module', including: tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.5.0, tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.6.0, tensorflow_gpu/python2/intel/0.7.1, etc.

The module I loaded is tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.6.0 and I used the examples of tensorflow at the version 0.6.0.

body:
Actually, I am using a server which bases on a lot of computers. And the administrators installed several versions of tensorflow as 'module', including: tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.5.0, tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.6.0, tensorflow_gpu/python2/intel/0.7.1, etc.

The module I loaded is tensorflow/python2/gcc/0.6.0 and I used the examples of tensorflow at the version 0.6.0.
